Package fr.xephi.authme.events

Class Summary
AuthMeTeleportEvent This event is call when AuthMe try to teleport a player
CustomEvent  
LoginEvent This event is called when a player login or register through AuthMe.
PasswordEncryptionEvent This event is called when we need to compare or get an hash password, for set a custom EncryptionMethod
ProtectInventoryEvent This event is call just after store inventory into cache and will empty the player inventory.
RegisterTeleportEvent This event is call if, and only if, a player is teleported just after a register.
ResetInventoryEvent This event is call when a creative inventory is reseted.
RestoreInventoryEvent This event restore the inventory from cache
SessionEvent This event is call when a player logging in through a timed session
SpawnTeleportEvent Called if a player is teleported to a specific spawn
StoreInventoryEvent This event is call just before write inventory content to cache
